---
// src/pages/index.astro
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Marquee from "@components/Marquee.astro";
import RoleSwitcher from "@components/RoleSwitcher.astro";
import Features from "@components/Features.astro";
const estiloTitulo =
  "text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif font-medium text-brand-text mb-6";
---

<Layout title="Mindesk | Gestión Clínica">
  <section class="relative min-h-dvh w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden px-4 sm:px-6 pt-24 md:pt-20 xl:pt-[18vh] pb-12">
  
    <div
      class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full"
    >
      <h1
        class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl md:text-[6.5rem] font-sans font-extrabold leading-[1.05] tracking-tighter text-[#2D3748] mb-6"
      >
        Tu mente en <br class="hidden sm:block" />
        <span class="text-[#10b981]"> el paciente </span>
      </h1>

      <p
        class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-800 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-snug font-sans font-medium tracking-tight"
      >
        Organiza tu gabinete, simplifica tu día. <br class="hidden sm:block" />
        Un entorno seguro para potenciar tu práctica.
      </p>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 w-full sm:w-auto mt-4 items-center font-sans"
      >
        <a
          href="/contacto"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-[#10b981] text-white font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_0_45px_rgba(16,185,129,0.5)] hover:shadow-[0_0_65px_rgba(16,185,129,0.7)] hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          Quiero Participar
        </a>

        <a
          href="/como-funciona"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-transparent text-slate-700 font-bold text-lg border-2 border-[#10b981] hover:bg-white hover:border-[#10b981] transition-all duration-300"
        >
          Ver cómo funciona
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 px-4 sm:px-6 w-full font-sans">
  
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16 md:mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-sans font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#2D3748] mb-6">
        El coste oculto de tu caos.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 font-medium tracking-tight">
        Identificamos los 3 ladrones de tiempo en tu consulta diaria.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8">

      <div class="group relative flex flex-col justify-between p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-linear-to-br from-white/40 to-white/5 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/60 shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.8),0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500 lg:row-span-2 overflow-hidden">
        
        <div class="flex flex-col h-full z-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/60 shadow-sm border border-white/80 rounded-full text-sm font-bold tracking-wide text-[#10b981]">01</span>
            
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#2D3748] mb-4 tracking-tight">Notas Dispersas</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 font-medium">
            La información de tus pacientes está repartida: documentos Word, hojas Excel, notas en papel. Recuperar el contexto de una sesión anterior te lleva más tiempo del que debería.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-auto w-full h-48 sm:h-56 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/20 border border-white/40 rounded-3xl backdrop-blur-sm transition-colors group-hover:bg-white/30"></div>
            
            <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 sm:top-6 sm:left-6 w-24 h-28 bg-blue-50/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-blue-200/60 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/5 -rotate-6 group-hover:-rotate-12 group-hover:-translate-x-3 group-hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 p-4 flex flex-col gap-2.5 z-10">
              <div class="w-1/2 h-2 bg-blue-300/60 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="w-full h-1.5 bg-blue-200/60 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="w-3/4 h-1.5 bg-blue-200/60 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="w-5/6 h-1.5 bg-blue-200/60 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 sm:bottom-6 sm:right-6 w-28 h-24 bg-emerald-50/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-emerald-200/60 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/5 rotate-6 group-hover:rotate-12 group-hover:translate-x-3 group-hover:translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 p-3.5 grid grid-cols-3 gap-1.5 z-20">
              <div class="h-2.5 bg-emerald-300/60 rounded-sm"></div>
              <div class="h-2.5 bg-emerald-200/60 rounded-sm"></div>
              <div class="h-2.5 bg-emerald-200/60 rounded-sm"></div>
              <div class="h-2.5 bg-emerald-200/60 rounded-sm"></div>
              <div class="h-2.5 bg-emerald-300/60 rounded-sm"></div>
              <div class="h-2.5 bg-emerald-200/60 rounded-sm"></div>
              <div class="h-2.5 bg-emerald-200/60 rounded-sm"></div>
              <div class="h-2.5 bg-emerald-200/60 rounded-sm"></div>
              <div class="h-2.5 bg-emerald-300/60 rounded-sm"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-24 h-24 bg-amber-50/90 backdrop-blur-xl border border-amber-200/60 rounded-xl shadow-xl shadow-amber-500/10 rotate-3 group-hover:-rotate-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500 p-3 flex flex-col items-center justify-center z-30">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-[3px] border-amber-200 border-t-amber-400 animate-spin"></div>
              <span class="text-[9px] font-bold text-amber-600 mt-3 tracking-widest uppercase">Buscando</span>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-8 p-8 rounded-4xl bg-linear-to-br from-white/40 to-white/5 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/60 shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.8),0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden">
        
        <div class="flex-1 z-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/60 shadow-sm border border-white/80 rounded-full text-sm font-bold tracking-wide text-[#10b981]">02</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#2D3748] mb-3 tracking-tight">Coordinación Caótica</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            Avisar al equipo de una cancelación, coordinar una derivación, compartir un recurso. La comunicación interna se convierte en un juego de WhatsApps cruzados.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full sm:w-48 h-32 bg-white/80 border border-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/50 -rotate-1 group-hover:-rotate-2 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 relative overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-sm">
          <!-- Fondo de caos -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-emerald-500/5 via-blue-500/5 to-purple-500/5"></div>
          
          <!-- Burbujas de mensajes superpuestas -->
          <div class="relative w-full h-full p-4 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2">
            
            <!-- Mensaje WhatsApp 1 (arriba izquierda) -->
            <div class="absolute top-3 left-3 w-20 h-8 bg-[#25D366] rounded-2xl rounded-bl-sm shadow-md flex items-center px-2 gap-1 -rotate-3 group-hover:-rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 bg-white/60 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 h-1 bg-white/40 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 h-1 bg-white/30 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Mensaje azul 2 (centro) -->
            <div class="absolute top-10 right-4 w-24 h-9 bg-blue-500 rounded-2xl rounded-br-sm shadow-md flex items-center px-2 gap-1 rotate-2 group-hover:rotate-4 transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 bg-white/60 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 h-1 bg-white/40 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="w-2 h-1 bg-white/30 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Mensaje WhatsApp 3 (abajo izquierda) -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-2 w-22 h-8 bg-[#25D366] rounded-2xl rounded-bl-sm shadow-md flex items-center px-2 gap-1 -rotate-2 group-hover:-rotate-4 transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="flex-1 h-1 bg-white/40 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="w-1 h-1 bg-white/60 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Mensaje morado 4 (derecha) -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 w-20 h-9 bg-purple-500 rounded-2xl rounded-br-sm shadow-md flex items-center px-2 gap-1 rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-5 transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="flex-1 h-1 bg-white/40 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 h-1 bg-white/30 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Badge de notificaciones en el centro -->
            <div class="relative z-10 w-12 h-12 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-xl border-2 border-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">24</span>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-8 p-8 rounded-4xl bg-linear-to-br from-white/40 to-white/5 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/60 shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.8),0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden">
        
        <div class="flex-1 z-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/60 shadow-sm border border-white/80 rounded-full text-sm font-bold tracking-wide text-[#10b981]">03</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#2D3748] mb-3 tracking-tight">Riesgo Legal</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            ¿Cumples el RGPD? Guardar datos sensibles en Excel sin encriptar es un peligro.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full sm:w-48 h-32 bg-linear-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 border border-red-200/60 rounded-3xl shadow-xl rotate-1 group-hover:rotate-2 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 relative flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Glow de alerta -->
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-24 h-24 bg-red-500/20 blur-xl"></div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center">
            <!-- Escudo roto (SVG) -->
            <svg width="48" height="52" viewBox="0 0 48 52" fill="none" class="mb-2">
              <!-- Escudo base partido -->
              <path d="M24 2 L42 10 L42 24 C42 36 32 46 24 50 C16 46 6 36 6 24 L6 10 Z" fill="#fecaca" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              
              <!-- Grieta diagonal -->
              <path d="M12 18 L36 42" stroke="#991b1b" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M10 16 L38 44" stroke="#7f1d1d" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.4"/>
              
              <!-- Símbolo de exclamación -->
              <circle cx="24" cy="22" r="2" fill="#991b1b"/>
              <rect x="22.5" y="28" width="3" height="8" rx="1.5" fill="#991b1b"/>
            </svg>

            <!-- Documentos escapándose -->
            <div class="absolute top-2 -left-1 w-8 h-10 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded shadow-md -rotate-12 opacity-80">
              <div class="p-1">
                <div class="h-0.5 w-4 bg-slate-300 rounded mb-0.5"></div>
                <div class="h-0.5 w-3 bg-slate-200 rounded mb-0.5"></div>
                <div class="h-0.5 w-3.5 bg-slate-200 rounded"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute top-1 -right-2 w-8 h-10 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded shadow-md rotate-15 opacity-70">
              <div class="p-1">
                <div class="h-0.5 w-4 bg-slate-300 rounded mb-0.5"></div>
                <div class="h-0.5 w-2.5 bg-slate-200 rounded mb-0.5"></div>
                <div class="h-0.5 w-3 bg-slate-200 rounded"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Badge VULNERABLE -->
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-red-600 tracking-widest bg-red-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-red-300 shadow-sm mt-1">
              VULNERABLE
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  <div id="demo">
    <RoleSwitcher />
  </div>

  <Features />

  <section class="py-16 md:py-28 px-4 sm:px-6 w-full font-sans overflow-hidden relative">

    <!-- Glow ambiental de fondo -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-150 h-100 bg-[#10b981]/6 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto relative z-10">

      <!-- Cabecera -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-sans font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#2D3748] mb-6">
          Tu acceso anticipado.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 font-medium tracking-tight">
          Únete ahora para moldear el futuro de la herramienta.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Hero card Beta -->
      <div class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] bg-linear-to-br from-white/60 to-white/20 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/70 shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.9),0_32px_80px_rgba(16,185,129,0.12),0_8px_32px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] overflow-hidden p-8 md:p-12">

        <!-- Glows internos -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-72 h-72 bg-[#10b981]/8 blur-[100px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-56 h-56 bg-[#b788f4]/6 blur-[80px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

        <!-- Fila superior: badge -->
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-8 sm:mb-10">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#10b981]/10 text-[#10b981] text-xs font-extrabold tracking-widest uppercase border border-[#10b981]/20">
            Beta Tester
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#b788f4]/10 text-[#b788f4] text-xs font-extrabold tracking-widest uppercase border border-[#b788f4]/20">
            Plazas limitadas
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Precio hero -->
        <div class="relative z-10 mb-3">
          <div class="flex items-end gap-4 mb-2">
            <span class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold text-[#2D3748] tracking-tighter leading-none">0€</span>
            <div class="mb-3 flex flex-col gap-1">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#10b981] uppercase tracking-wide">Durante la Beta</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium text-base">Ayúdanos a mejorar y obtén grandes ventajas</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Divisor -->
        <div class="relative z-10 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-slate-200 to-transparent my-8"></div>

        <!-- Features en dos columnas -->
        <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#10b981]/10 border border-[#10b981]/25 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-[#10b981]" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="1,4 3.5,6.5 9,1"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-extrabold text-[#2D3748]">Acceso completo</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium">Todas las funciones desde el día 1</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#10b981]/10 border border-[#10b981]/25 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-[#10b981]" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="1,4 3.5,6.5 9,1"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-extrabold text-[#2D3748]">Prioridad total</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium">Tu voz moldea el producto</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#10b981]/10 border border-[#10b981]/25 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-[#10b981]" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="1,4 3.5,6.5 9,1"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-extrabold text-[#2D3748]">Línea directa</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium">Contacto directo con los fundadores</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#10b981]/10 border border-[#10b981]/25 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-[#10b981]" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="1,4 3.5,6.5 9,1"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-extrabold text-[#2D3748]">30% de descuento</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium">Durante los primeros 6 meses al lanzar</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center">
          <a href="/contacto" class="w-full sm:flex-1 py-4 rounded-2xl bg-[#10b981] hover:bg-[#0ea572] hover:-translate-y-0.5 text-white font-extrabold text-center transition-all duration-200 shadow-[0_8px_32px_rgba(16,185,129,0.35)] hover:shadow-[0_12px_40px_rgba(16,185,129,0.5)] text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
            Solicitar Acceso Beta
          </a>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium text-center sm:text-left sm:max-w-35 leading-relaxed">Sin tarjeta.<br/>Sin compromisos.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-28 px-4 sm:px-6 w-full font-sans overflow-hidden relative">

    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-125 h-100 bg-[#b788f4]/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto relative z-10">

      <!-- Cabecera -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-sans font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#2D3748] mb-6">
          ¿Tienes dudas?<br/>Nosotros resolvemos.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 font-medium tracking-tight">
          Las preguntas que nos hace todo el mundo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQs -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">

        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <details class="group rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-br from-white/80 to-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/80 shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.9),0_4px_24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-3 px-4 sm:px-7 py-5 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden list-none">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-xl font-extrabold text-[#2D3748] tracking-tight leading-snug">¿Tengo que introducir datos de mis pacientes?</h3>
            <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/60 border border-white/80 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 group-open:bg-[#10b981] group-open:border-[#10b981]">
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-slate-400 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 group-open:text-white" viewBox="0 0 12 8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="1,1.5 6,6.5 11,1.5"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-4 sm:px-7 pb-6">
            <div class="h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-slate-200/80 to-transparent mb-5"></div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed text-base">
              Mejor que no. Queremos que explores la herramienta con total libertad y cero riesgos. Durante esta fase Beta, usarás datos ficticios — nombres inventados o iniciales. Así podrás <strong class="text-[#2D3748]">probar todas las funciones</strong>, simular sesiones y trastear con la plataforma sin comprometer la confidencialidad de tu consulta. La migración de datos reales la haremos juntos cuando lancemos la versión final.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <details class="group rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-br from-white/80 to-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/80 shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.9),0_4px_24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-3 px-4 sm:px-7 py-5 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden list-none">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-xl font-extrabold text-[#2D3748] tracking-tight leading-snug">¿Por qué dedicar tiempo a una Beta si no puedo llevar mi consulta real?</h3>
